title: 169: The Aldi Haul Episode (April '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Aldi Haul Episode (April '22 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa, Jamie & Mikey are trying some killer finds, like a yummy shepherd’s pie, the best chickenless tenders ever, amazing artichoke-stuffed chicken, a super creamy and tasty tzatziki dip, and SO MUCH MORE. Plus, the find of the entire haul: bacon habanero pretzel slims that are OUT OF THIS WORLD! Wait no more, push play now, then when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products!
itunes:summary: Get ready for an Aldi “Hauldi” that has 11 stellar finds you need to add to your Aldi shopping list ASAP!
